PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783707575
OL,3,CPolice marksman who shot Chris Kaba
OL,4,Cwill not face misconduct probe
OL,6,FThe police marksman who shot Chris
OL,7,FKaba will no longer face misconduct
OL,8,Fproceedings after the Government
OL,9,Fchanged regulations around officers'
OL,10,Fuse of force.
OL,12,FMartyn Blake shot the 24-year-old in
OL,13,FStreatham, south-east London, in 2022
OL,14,Fafter he tried to ram his way past
OL,15,Fpolice cars.
OL,17,FThe officer was cleared of murder by a
OL,18,Fjury at the Old Bailey, with fellow
OL,19,Fpolice marksmen enraged that he had
OL,20,Ffaced charges.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783707575
OL,3,CPolice marksman who shot Chris Kaba
OL,4,Cwill not face misconduct probe
OL,6,FSgt Blake was still due to face
OL,7,Fmisconduct proceedings, but watchdog
OL,8,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,9,FConduct (IOPC) paused the process
OL,10,Fwhile it waited for Government
OL,11,Fregulation changes to be published.
OL,13,FOn Wednesday it announced that Sgt
OL,14,FBlake will no longer face misconduct
OL,15,Fproceedings, with dozens of other non-
OL,16,Ffatal use of force cases in England
OL,17,Fand Wales also expected to be affected
OL,18,Fif forces take the same approach.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783707575
OL,3,CPolice marksman who shot Chris Kaba
OL,4,Cwill not face misconduct probe
OL,6,FIOPC director of strategy and policy
OL,7,FAndrew Johnson said: "We carefully
OL,8,Fconsidered the law change and its
OL,9,Fstated intent to address the perceived
OL,10,Funfairness and lack of proportionality
OL,11,Fof the civil law test.
OL,13,F"We believe this position provides
OL,14,Fconsistency across impacted cases and
OL,15,Fis fair to officers who are facing
OL,16,Fpotential dismissal for misconduct,
OL,17,Fwhich if it occurred now, would not
OL,18,Famount to misconduct under the new law.
OL,26,@oD@VOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783707575
OL,3,CPolice marksman who shot Chris Kaba
OL,4,Cwill not face misconduct probe
OL,6,F"We expect the number of relevant
OL,7,Fcases that are affected by this law
OL,8,Fchange to be relatively small."
OL,10,FAfter Sgt Blake's acquittal, then-home
OL,11,Fsecretary Yvette Cooper vowed to raise
OL,12,Fthe legal test used by prosecutors to
OL,13,Fdetermine whether to bring charges
OL,14,Fagainst police officers over use of
OL,15,Fforce into line with the standard used
OL,16,Ffor members of the public.
OL,18,FThe test used by the IOPC over whether
OL,19,Fto bring misconduct proceedings would
OL,20,Falso be raised to the level used in
OL,21,Fcriminal law, she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783707575
OL,3,CPolice marksman who shot Chris Kaba
OL,4,Cwill not face misconduct probe
OL,6,FMetropolitan Police Deputy
OL,7,FCommissioner Matt Jukes said acquittal
OL,8,Fafter a criminal trial should have
OL,9,Fbrought the case to "a clear and
OL,10,Fdefinitive conclusion".
OL,12,FHe said: "We recognise the impact on
OL,13,FNX121, his family and the wider
OL,14,Ffirearms community, who have endured
OL,15,Falmost four years of uncertainty while
OL,16,Fthese processes have unfolded, as well
OL,17,Fas the family of Chris Kaba, who
OL,18,Fcontinue to live with the loss of a
OL,19,Floved one.
OL,26,@qD@UOUrD@VO]tD@JOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783707575
OL,3,CPolice marksman who shot Chris Kaba
OL,4,Cwill not face misconduct probe
OL,6,F"We have consistently said since the
OL,7,Fcriminal trial that there is no basis
OL,8,Ffor further action against this
OL,9,Fofficer and that remains our position.
OL,11,F"I know this change will also provide
OL,12,Freassurance to firearms officers
OL,13,Facross London and the wider country,
OL,14,Fwho carry immense responsibility on
OL,15,Fbehalf of the public and need
OL,16,Fconfidence that decisions made in good
OL,17,Ffaith, in fast-moving and dangerous
OL,18,Fsituations, will be judged fairly.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783707575
OL,3,CPolice marksman who shot Chris Kaba
OL,4,Cwill not face misconduct probe
OL,6,F"At the same time, this case has
OL,7,Fexposed that the current system is too
OL,8,Fslow. A split-second decision, taken
OL,9,Fin circumstances which presented an
OL,10,Fimmediate threat, has been followed by
OL,11,Fyears of investigations and legal
OL,12,Fproceedings.
OL,14,F"That has had a profound impact on
OL,15,Feveryone involved and demonstrates the
OL,16,Fneed that both policing and the IOPC
OL,17,Frecognise for a swifter system that
OL,18,Fmaintains both public confidence and
OL,19,Frigorous accountability.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783707575
OL,3,CPolice marksman who shot Chris Kaba
OL,4,Cwill not face misconduct probe
OL,6,F"That is why I welcome the recent
OL,7,Fchanges to the law, introducing a
OL,8,Fpresumption of anonymity for firearms
OL,9,Fofficers during court proceedings
OL,10,Funtil conviction and restoring the
OL,11,Fcriminal test for the use of force in
OL,12,Fmisconduct cases."
OL,14,FOn the night Mr Kaba died, police had
OL,15,Ffollowed and penned in the Audi that
OL,16,Fhe was driving because it had been
OL,17,Flinked to three previous firearms
OL,18,Fincidents in five months.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783707575
OL,3,CPolice marksman who shot Chris Kaba
OL,4,Cwill not face misconduct probe
OL,6,FThey were not aware of his identity at
OL,7,Fthe time, but Mr Kaba was a member of
OL,8,Fone of London's most violent street
OL,9,Fgangs and was accused of being
OL,10,Finvolved in two shootings in the six
OL,11,Fdays before he died.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
